direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **test-plan-analyze-endpoints**
  LLM sub-agent (Sonnet)

  - receives file paths from orchestrator
  - context: fork
  - allowed tools: Read
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Read Inputs ---

read-inputs: |md
  **Read Source Documents**

  - strategy files (strat-tasks/)
  - ADR files (if provided)
  - additional docs (API spec, design doc)
  - ONLY files specified in arguments
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Extract Scope ---

extract-scope: |md
  **Extract Feature Scope**
  LLM analysis

  - purpose: what + why from strategy
  - in-scope: testing responsibilities
  - out-of-scope: explicit exclusions only
  - test objectives: 3-7 from acceptance criteria
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Extract Endpoints ---

extract-endpoints: |md
  **Extract Testable Interfaces**
  LLM analysis

  - REST endpoints (path, method)
  - gRPC services / RPC methods
  - Python/Go methods
  - UI components, CLI commands
  - CRDs, ConfigMaps, env vars
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Prioritize ---

prioritize: |md
  **Assign Priorities**

  - P0: core functionality
  - P1: important user-facing
  - P2: edge cases, advanced
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Gap Analysis ---

gap-analysis: |md
  **Identify Gaps**

  - flag ambiguous items
  - note missing endpoint details
  - specify resolving doc type
  - (ADR / API spec / design doc)
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Output ---

output: |md
  **Structured Output**

  - Section 1: Scope Analysis
  - Section 4: Endpoints table
  - Pending details list
  - Gaps with resolution paths
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Orchestrator ---

orchestrator: |md
  **test-plan-create**
  (orchestrator)
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# --- Output callout ---

output-format: |md
  ## Scope Analysis
  ### Purpose / In Scope / Out of Scope
  ### Test Objectives (3-7)
  ## Endpoints/Methods Under Test
  Endpoint / Type / Purpose / Priority
  ### Pending Details
  ## Gaps
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#bbbbbb"
  style.stroke-width: 1
  style.font: mono
  style.font-size: 10
}

# --- Flow ---

orchestrator -> entry: "file paths"
entry -> read-inputs
read-inputs -> extract-scope: "strategy + ADR content"
extract-scope -> extract-endpoints
extract-endpoints -> prioritize
prioritize -> gap-analysis
gap-analysis -> output

output -> output-format: {
  style.stroke: "#bbbbbb"
  style.stroke-dash: 4
  style.stroke-width: 1
}
